relevant_findings.HEENT: + scleral icterus and + jaundice, mucous membranes moist.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs/gallops/rubs.
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes/rales/rhonchi.
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, mildly distended, + mild tenderness to palpation in the right upper quadrant (RUQ) and left upper quadrant (LUQ), no rebound tenderness, no masses palpated.
relevant_findings.extremities: No edema, warm and well perfused.
